data.description: Strong and Energy efficient, CONCRETE REINFORCED FOAM BLOCK CONSTRUCTION 9' ceilings. Floor plan that offers a living/dining combination with bay window in living room. Kitchen bar, ample cabinet and counter space, the kitchen provides the perfect set up for entertaining! Inside laundry area. Tile floors in main living area, halls and baths. Nice sized bedrooms, your guest bath has a tub/shower combination while your master bath has dual sinks and a shower. Great architectural touches like arched doorways and recessed lighting. Screened back porch with privacy fenced back yard. Has in wall pest control system. Gated community with private streets,  lighting, underground electricity, pool, jacuzzi, playground. Close to schools, shopping, downtown, medical facilities. No age restrictions.
